1
00:00:00,060 --> 00:00:02,790
(The following content may not be
suitable for viewers under 15.)

2
00:00:02,790 --> 00:00:04,230
(Viewer discretion is advised.)

3
00:00:05,550 --> 00:00:07,310
Park Hae Joo...

4
00:00:07,720 --> 00:00:09,980
transferred from Seyeon
Girls High School...

5
00:00:09,980 --> 00:00:12,720
in Hyehwa-dong in Seoul.

6
00:00:13,650 --> 00:00:16,770
Her father is a professor...

7
00:00:17,390 --> 00:00:21,230
at Seoul University. He is a great man.

8
00:00:21,890 --> 00:00:24,070
- Seoul University?
- Really?

9
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:25,310
Quiet.

10
00:00:25,700 --> 00:00:28,310
Moreover, Hae Joo...

11
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:30,340
has been top of her class...

12
00:00:30,540 --> 00:00:32,810
the entire time at Seyeon.

13
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:34,740
- Top of her class.
- Wow.

14
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:37,880
As the top student at her last school...

15
00:00:39,150 --> 00:00:40,410
Well...

16
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:44,060
Compared to you stupid
pigs whose grades stink,

17
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:47,020
she will be the model student.

18
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:49,300
We have high hopes for her.

19
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:53,460
Okay, Hae Joo.

20
00:00:53,870 --> 00:00:54,960
Say something.

21
00:01:03,270 --> 00:01:06,100
Don't mind those punks.

22
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:08,010
Speak comfortably.

23
00:01:09,910 --> 00:01:11,010
Sir.

24
00:01:11,790 --> 00:01:13,880
I feel bad introducing myself...

25
00:01:14,410 --> 00:01:17,990
while my friends are being punished.

26
00:01:18,230 --> 00:01:20,430
I'd like you to let them sit back down.

27
00:01:22,850 --> 00:01:25,290
Wow. She's got guts.

28
00:01:25,570 --> 00:01:27,600
- Wow.
- Seriously.

29
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,260
Oh my gosh.

30
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,840
Hae Joo,

31
00:01:35,180 --> 00:01:38,480
not only are you smart,
you have a heart of gold.

32
00:01:40,370 --> 00:01:43,510
You guys lucked out because of Hae Joo.

33
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:45,850
Get down.

34
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:58,260
Jung Hee. You punk. What are you doing?

35
00:01:58,260 --> 00:02:00,040
Hey, Jung Hee.

36
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,340
Come down.

37
00:02:03,660 --> 00:02:04,740
Come down.

38
00:02:11,110 --> 00:02:12,240
Thank you.

39
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,090
Hello.

40
00:02:17,390 --> 00:02:19,180
I'm Park Hae Joo.

41
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:22,120
I'm not a genius,

42
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:24,220
or a model student.

43
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:27,990
I'm an average student who likes...

44
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:30,990
Sanulrim, Hae Eun Hee, and the Beatles.

45
00:02:31,830 --> 00:02:32,960
Also,

46
00:02:33,530 --> 00:02:35,270
one day,

47
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:38,240
I want to experience passionate love.

48
00:02:39,670 --> 00:02:42,840
I am a hot-blooded woman.

49
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:47,210
Yes.

50
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:55,150
- It's nice to meet you.
- Welcome.

51
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:07,990
(Episode 2)

52
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:12,710
Did you see Hae Joo's skin?

53
00:03:12,870 --> 00:03:14,270
Is it because she's from Seoul?

54
00:03:14,530 --> 00:03:17,500
She has incredibly nice skin.

55
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:19,370
She's pretty too.

56
00:03:20,020 --> 00:03:21,840
She kind of looks like Jang Mee Hee.

57
00:03:22,650 --> 00:03:25,150
No way. She looks like Im Ye Jin.

58
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:28,560
Whatever. Im Ye Jin would cry out in anger.

59
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:30,120
Im Ye Jin? Whatever.

60
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:33,090
She looks like Bae Yun Jung.

61
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:35,520
- The comedian?
- Yes.

62
00:03:35,690 --> 00:03:38,330
- No way.
- That's not true.

63
00:03:38,330 --> 00:03:40,430
- Not Bae Yun Jung.
- No way.

64
00:03:40,430 --> 00:03:42,460
What? She has eyes like this...

65
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:44,560
- just like Bae Yun Jung.
- No way.

66
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:50,900
Hi. You're the girl from yesterday,

67
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:52,680
right?

68
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,580
What?

69
00:04:00,020 --> 00:04:01,180
Do you know her?

70
00:04:01,490 --> 00:04:02,960
How's your knee?

71
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:04,620
It didn't get infected?

72
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:07,060
No.

73
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:10,930
I'm glad. My dad and I were worried.

74
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,930
Jung Hee?

75
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:16,100
Hi, Jung Hee.

76
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:18,470
Let's be friends.

77
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:25,570
Hey. Jung Hee.

78
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:30,050
That's right. We have history class.

79
00:04:31,380 --> 00:04:33,310
I didn't do my homework.

80
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:35,810
That's right.

81
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:46,930
What?

82
00:04:47,370 --> 00:04:49,240
We didn't even go in.

83
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,110
You're being so mean.

84
00:04:51,110 --> 00:04:52,410
What?

85
00:04:54,610 --> 00:04:55,980
What are they doing?

86
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:57,440
We didn't do anything.

87
00:04:57,550 --> 00:05:00,240
Jung Hee, isn't that your brother?

88
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:03,940
- Dong Moon is here too.
- Fish Head is here too.

89
00:05:04,420 --> 00:05:05,640
What are they doing?

90
00:05:06,050 --> 00:05:08,160
Hey! Here she comes!

91
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,880
- Yes.
- She's coming!

92
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,160
She's here.

93
00:05:14,990 --> 00:05:16,930
Are they all here to see Hae Joo?

94
00:05:17,390 --> 00:05:18,560
They are.

95
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:21,040
I guess word got out that a pretty girl...

96
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,700
transferred here from Seoul.

97
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:26,700
What pretty girl?

98
00:05:28,330 --> 00:05:29,410
Let's go.

99
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:34,370
Hi, Jung Hee. You just finished?

100
00:05:34,570 --> 00:05:36,880
Aren't you going down there?

101
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,880
Not me. I'm here...

102
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,560
to see you.

103
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,680
Don't.

104
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:48,530
Jung Hee. We'll go first.

105
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:51,120
Wait for me! Eun Ja!

106
00:05:53,740 --> 00:05:55,830
What? Do you need to talk to me?

107
00:05:58,540 --> 00:05:59,560
Well...

108
00:06:00,930 --> 00:06:03,370
- The thing is...
- If not, I'm leaving.

109
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,010
Jung Hee.

110
00:06:08,180 --> 00:06:10,440
Aren't you hungry? Want to get pastries?

111
00:06:10,740 --> 00:06:12,180
I got my allowance.

112
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,990
I don't like pastries.

113
00:06:13,990 --> 00:06:17,160
Then do you want tempura? Spicy rice cakes?

114
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,060
Eat by yourself.

115
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:21,430
I'm busy, so bye.

116
00:06:23,890 --> 00:06:24,990
Jung Hee.

117
00:06:27,130 --> 00:06:29,260
Why is she always so busy?

118
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:51,430
Excuse me. Didn't we meet...

119
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:53,530
yesterday at the intersection?

120
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:54,930
The pharmacy.

121
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:59,030
Yes. Hello.

122
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:00,190
Hello.

123
00:07:01,890 --> 00:07:03,040
A junior?

124
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:06,170
- Yes.
- Then I'm older.

125
00:07:06,330 --> 00:07:08,680
I'm Son Jin, a senior at Gyeryoon.

126
00:07:08,700 --> 00:07:11,000
May I speak casually to you?

127
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,730
Anyway, the thing is...

128
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,370
If you have any questions...

129
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:37,040
or need help with anything, call me.

130
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,430
But...

131
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,940
Okay. Goodbye.

132
00:07:53,010 --> 00:07:54,010
See you.

133
00:07:56,220 --> 00:07:57,790
Hey. Jung Hee.

134
00:07:57,790 --> 00:07:59,750
Is it true? The cosmos
flower is in your class?

135
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:00,930
Cosmos?

136
00:08:00,930 --> 00:08:04,800
You know, the new girl that moved recently.

137
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,040
Cosmos? What garbage.

138
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,040
I was worried...

139
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:11,610
because I thought Cosmos was older than me.

140
00:08:12,410 --> 00:08:14,180
How lucky. Bring her home.

141
00:08:14,180 --> 00:08:15,330
What? Why?

142
00:08:15,330 --> 00:08:16,330
What do you mean?

143
00:08:16,810 --> 00:08:19,550
Your big brother wants to get close to her.

144
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:23,440
Hey, Bong Soo. I saw you
camped outside my school.

145
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,440
Get it together...

146
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:26,510
before I tell Father.

147
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,450
Tell me what?

148
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:33,190
Hello, Father.

149
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:36,320
Tell me. What?

150
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,190
It's nothing.

151
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:39,690
- It's nothing?
- No.

152
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,000
Okay.

153
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:44,930
Why are you always bugging your brother?

154
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:47,330
You wench.

155
00:08:47,570 --> 00:08:50,810
You couldn't be born a boy like Bong Soo.

156
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:52,510
Go inside.

157
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:55,520
Have a nice day!

158
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,520
Sure.

159
00:08:57,310 --> 00:08:58,390
Jung Hee.

160
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:01,760
- Jung Hee.
- Jung Hee!

161
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,450
Yes?

162
00:09:03,450 --> 00:09:04,680
Show him respect.

163
00:09:05,530 --> 00:09:07,430
Get home safely, Father.

164
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,320
Jung Hee.

165
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,360
Jung Hee.

166
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:13,770
Hi, number three.

167
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:15,640
Jung Hee. Hey!

168
00:09:16,090 --> 00:09:17,560
Cosmos?

169
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:24,050
Jung Hee. Cosmos.

170
00:09:24,050 --> 00:09:26,070
- She's in your class.
- Get out of here!

171
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:28,420
Mom! Jung Hee is hitting me!

172
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,750
What Cosmos?

173
00:09:40,190 --> 00:09:42,160
Hae Joo, that Seoul chick,

174
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,400
is getting on my nerves.

175
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:58,180
What's so pretty about the Seoul chick?

176
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:02,180
I'm much prettier.

177
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:08,060
(September 10, 1979)

178
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,390
When will Sunday come?

179
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,400
I miss Jin.

180
00:10:16,430 --> 00:10:19,170
- All right.
- What did you bring?

181
00:10:22,170 --> 00:10:23,770
Jin.

182
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:26,460
Jung Hee, let's eat our yummy food.

183
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:28,070
I'm not hungry.

184
00:10:28,070 --> 00:10:30,100
Don't you have a broadcast today?

185
00:10:31,650 --> 00:10:34,680
We're taking turns starting this week.

186
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:39,750
Where did the Seoul chick go?

187
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:41,920
This is JHBS,

188
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,290
Jeonghyeon's broadcasting club.

189
00:10:44,660 --> 00:10:46,800
We will now begin the afternoon broadcast.

190
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:48,900
Hello,

191
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,860
my fellow students.

192
00:10:51,430 --> 00:10:54,230
The canna flowers that
graced the streets...

193
00:10:54,230 --> 00:10:56,300
have shed their petals...

194
00:10:56,300 --> 00:11:00,640
Isn't that the Seoul chick?

195
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:02,330
But the club president
was supposed to do it.

196
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:03,650
Were you surprised by the unfamiliar voice?

197
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:08,280
I'm one of your afternoon broadcasters.

198
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:11,110
My name is Park Hae Joo.

199
00:11:11,920 --> 00:11:14,520
I'm nervous because it's
my first broadcast.

200
00:11:14,980 --> 00:11:17,260
It would be very encouraging...

201
00:11:17,260 --> 00:11:19,450
if you'd cheer me on.

202
00:11:20,060 --> 00:11:21,190
Jung Hee.

203
00:11:22,450 --> 00:11:25,720
Didn't you say you'd do the broadcast?

204
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:29,190
Carpenters' "Top of the World".

205
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,330
"Top of the World". Awesome!

206
00:11:34,470 --> 00:11:36,550
I was going to,

207
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:39,410
but I'm a senior now, so
it's sort of a burden.

208
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:41,880
- Was I okay?
- How is Hae Joo...

209
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:44,180
in our broadcasting club?

210
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:46,790
She was the DJ at her old school.

211
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:50,080
The club president there
is my junior high friend.

212
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,720
She recommended her.

213
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:01,230
Why was our schedule changed again?

214
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:04,360
The instructor is going
somewhere for training.

215
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:06,780
Change quickly!

216
00:12:07,070 --> 00:12:10,550
If you're late, you have to take 10 laps.

217
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:12,440
- You know that, right?
- What's this?

218
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,780
Where's my gym uniform?

219
00:12:13,780 --> 00:12:15,780
Look carefully.

220
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:19,050
Hurry it up!

221
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:28,130
Hey. Look at the Seoul chick.

222
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,320
A strappy undershirt?

223
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:35,730
Wow. Ae Sook's strappy undershirt...

224
00:12:35,730 --> 00:12:37,810
doesn't even compare.

225
00:12:40,540 --> 00:12:43,910
You said only delinquents
wear strappy ones, right?

226
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:45,550
Is she a one too?

227
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:49,840
Who knows? Maybe she is a total delinquent.

228
00:12:50,580 --> 00:12:52,940
Where is my gym uniform?

229
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:56,420
Attention!

230
00:12:58,530 --> 00:13:05,320
At... Ease!

231
00:13:07,040 --> 00:13:08,090
You two.

232
00:13:08,830 --> 00:13:09,860
Get up here.

233
00:13:10,310 --> 00:13:11,540
Get up here!

234
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,180
Jung Hee.

235
00:13:22,380 --> 00:13:24,790
Why are you dressed like that?

236
00:13:25,310 --> 00:13:28,260
I lost my gym uniform top.

237
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:31,580
- And you?
- I just transferred,

238
00:13:31,580 --> 00:13:33,450
so I do not have it yet.

239
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:36,160
Being a transfer student...

240
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:37,770
is an excuse!

241
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:41,640
How could a soldier enter a war...

242
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:43,860
without her uniform?

243
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:46,780
I tried to borrow one from another class,

244
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:49,880
but our class schedule
was suddenly changed,

245
00:13:50,050 --> 00:13:52,250
so I did not have time to borrow one.

246
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,840
- That is unacceptable.
- She is pretty.

247
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:58,420
Make the impossible possible.

248
00:13:58,810 --> 00:14:01,110
Don't you know that is the attitude...

249
00:14:01,110 --> 00:14:05,320
the youth must live by in this new era?

250
00:14:05,350 --> 00:14:06,500
We do know!

251
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:09,090
Why aren't you answering?

252
00:14:09,350 --> 00:14:11,060
I think...

253
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:14,270
trying to force something
that is impossible...

254
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:16,770
to make it happen is reckless.

255
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:22,200
- What?
- Rather,

256
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:26,380
I think trying my best
in something I can do...

257
00:14:26,380 --> 00:14:28,650
is much more productive.

258
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:40,090
Two of you.

259
00:14:41,130 --> 00:14:43,630
Take 10 laps around the field.

260
00:14:43,630 --> 00:14:45,560
That's not fair.

261
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:47,330
Shall I make it 100?

262
00:14:50,330 --> 00:14:51,540
I'll run.

263
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:55,780
What are you doing?

264
00:15:04,180 --> 00:15:05,480
Stay in line!

265
00:15:05,610 --> 00:15:07,660
If either of you stops,

266
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:11,430
you'll have to run 200 laps!

267
00:15:12,630 --> 00:15:13,630
Attention!

268
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:16,300
At ease!

269
00:15:27,570 --> 00:15:28,830
Poor Jung Hee.

270
00:15:28,830 --> 00:15:31,180
What if she faints?

271
00:15:31,810 --> 00:15:32,910
Gosh.

272
00:15:34,070 --> 00:15:35,150
What?

273
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:42,920
Hey. Ae Sook.

274
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,890
Oh Man Sang wants you in
the teacher's office.

275
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:55,300
Ae Sook.

276
00:15:55,830 --> 00:15:58,440
You smoked in the bathroom
at Ahram Church, right?

277
00:15:59,070 --> 00:16:00,140
I did not.

278
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:03,740
Yes, you did. There was a witness.

279
00:16:04,180 --> 00:16:05,540
Darn it.

280
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:07,050
Did Jung Hee tattle on me?

281
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:09,180
"Did Jung Hee tattle on me?"

282
00:16:09,210 --> 00:16:12,350
