357
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:49,290
Auntie. Don't be good to that gangster.

358
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:52,660
You watch yourself too.

359
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:54,830
- What did I do?
- Still,

360
