00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:44,950
they're coming here tomorrow afternoon.

566
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:47,350
With their student body president.

567
00:36:47,350 --> 00:36:48,850
The student body president?

568
00:36:49,050 --> 00:36:50,360
As in, Son Jin?

569
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:51,620
Yes.

570
00:36:51,890 --> 00:36:53,890
I'm going crazy.

571
00:36:53,890 --> 00:36:55,260
Yes.

572
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:57,330
- Jin?
- Son Jin is coming?

573
00:36:57,330 --> 00:37:00,130
- He's coming here?
- My heart is racing.

574
00:37:00,130 --> 00:37:02,130
This is a chance of a lifetime.

575
00:37:02,130 --> 00:37:03,900
That's right.

576
00:37:04,040 --> 00:37:05,500
While preparing the show,

577
00:37:05,500 --> 00:37:08,940
you and Jin can naturally...

578
00:37:09,570 --> 00:37:11,380
get closer.

579
00:37:12,940 --> 00:37:14,250
It's too soon to relax.

580
00:37:14,580 --> 00:37:16,620
- Why?
- Hae Joo.

581
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:19,990
That pretty Seoul girl may be an obstacle.

582
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,520
What do you mean?

583
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:23,920
Hae Joo and I are friends now.

584
00:37:24,460 --> 00:37:26,060
She'd never do that.

585
00:37:26,090 --> 00:37:29,460
What does it matter if she's good?

586
00:37:29,530 --> 00:37:31,800
How could you say that...

587
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:34,800
after seeing the mob outside the school?

588
00:37:40,970 --> 00:37:42,240
You're right.

589
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:44,080
All boys are the same.

590
00:37:44,080 --> 00:37:45,980
If they see a pretty girl,

591
00:37:45,980 --> 00:37:48,880
they become complete idiots.

592
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:50,580
Then what?

593
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:53,950
What if Son Jin falls for Hae Joo too?

594
00:37:54,420 --> 00:37:55,620
What?

595
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:06,630
Jin.

596
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:15,040
He can't!

597
00:38:15,270 --> 00:38:17,510
- That's right. He can't.
- That's right. He can't.

598
00:38:17,810 --> 00:38:19,040
There's only one way.

599
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,110
The Jang Hui Bin tactic.

600
00:38:21,350 --> 00:38:22,750
The Jang Hui Bin tactic?

601
00:38:22,810 --> 00:38:25,420
Jang Hui Bin hid all the
pretty court ladies...

602
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:27,520
where the king couldn't see them.

603
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:29,590
In case the king...

604
00:38:30,190 --> 00:38:31,690
would like them?

605
00:38:31,890 --> 00:38:33,260
- That's right.
- Then...

606
00:38:33,590 --> 00:38:35,830
we should hide Hae Joo where Jin...

607
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:37,630
won't see her?

608
00:38:38,430 --> 00:38:39,830
No.

609
00:38:40,200 --> 00:38:42,270
I can't do something so cheap.

610
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:44,940
Do you want to lose him?

611
00:38:45,340 --> 00:38:48,370
Still. I can't do that.

612
00:38:49,570 --> 00:38:51,410
Don't get blood on your hands.

613
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:54,680
We'll do it in the name of friendship.

614
00:38:59,790 --> 00:39:01,220
Where's Hae Joo?

615
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:06,120
There was some stuff in our class.

616
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:07,190
Really?

617
00:39:07,530 --> 00:39:10,430
Why today? The Gyeryoon
guys are coming today.

618
00:39:15,630 --> 00:39:16,800
(Self Study)

619
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:18,040
Look at you.

620
00:39:18,470 --> 00:39:20,340
Sit straight.

621
00:39:20,810 --> 00:39:23,180
- X becomes...
- I should kill you.

622
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:25,340
Do you understand?

623
00:39:26,510 --> 00:39:28,380
I get it now.

624
00:39:28,610 --> 00:39:30,450
I couldn't understand a thing...

625
00:39:30,450 --> 00:39:32,620
when Eun Ja tried to teach me.

626
00:39:32,850 --> 00:39:34,490
Now, I get it.

627
00:39:35,220 --> 00:39:36,250
Good.

628
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:39,260
What do you need?

629
00:39:41,430 --> 00:39:42,830
Thanks, Hae Joo.

630
00:39:43,030 --> 00:39:46,600
If we don't get their math grades up,

631
00:39:46,770 --> 00:39:49,430
Mr. Oh said he'd kill us all too.

632
00:39:51,370 --> 00:39:52,400
Hae Joo.

633
00:39:52,770 --> 00:39:54,570
Don't you have to go to
the broadcasting club?

634
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:56,240
Oh no.

635
00:39:56,910 --> 00:39:59,140
- I'm late.
- Hae Joo.

636
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:01,210
Can you teach me this too?

637
00:40:01,210 --> 00:40:03,150
Wait. Me too. Me too.

638
00:40:03,150 --> 00:40:04,920
I need help with so many problems.

639
00:40:07,050 --> 00:40:09,090
This isn't right.

640
00:40:11,290 --> 00:40:12,490
Jung Hee.

641
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:15,630
This goes against your fair-play attitude.

642
00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:18,760
They're coming!

643
00:40:19,130 --> 00:40:20,770
- They're coming.
- Really?

644
00:40:20,770 --> 00:40:22,630
- He's really cute.
- Wow.

645
00:40:24,470 --> 00:40:27,540
- He really handsome.
- He is.

646
00:40:27,940 --> 00:40:29,370
He's so good-looking.

647
00:40:29,740 --> 00:40:32,410
- Jin.
- He's so good-looking.

648
00:40:35,310 --> 00:40:37,320
- Hello.
- Nice to meet you.

649
00:40:37,950 --> 00:40:40,050
- Hello.
- Hello.

650
00:40:40,450 --> 00:40:42,250
- Hello.
- Hello.

651
00:40:42,350 --> 00:40:44,320
Hello. It's nice to meet you.

652
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:48,030
- Hello.
- Hello.

653
00:40:48,060 --> 00:40:49,260
Jin.

654
00:40:49,860 --> 00:40:52,230
Are you ignoring me?

655
00:40:56,370 --> 00:40:57,470
We meet again.

656
00:40:59,200 --> 00:41:00,540
This must be fate.

657
00:41:05,440 --> 00:41:08,880
We're estimating about 150 people.

658
00:41:09,250 --> 00:41:10,750
- 150?
- Yes.

659
00:41:11,080 --> 00:41:13,790
Let's use the auditorium
here for the venue.

660
00:41:13,950 --> 00:41:17,060
"Fate." He said it was fate.

661
00:41:17,390 --> 00:41:18,820
What could he mean?

662
00:41:19,220 --> 00:41:22,030
Did he miss me too?

663
00:41:22,490 --> 00:41:23,930
Does he...

664
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:32,600
I think we have about a week left.

665
00:41:32,900 --> 00:41:34,670
Jung Hee...

666
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:36,910
should be with Jin by now, right?

667
00:41:37,010 --> 00:41:40,010
She must be so grateful for our friendship,

668
00:41:40,050 --> 00:41:43,380
since we're holding Hae Joo here like this.

669
00:41:50,420 --> 00:41:51,660
Where's Hae Joo?

670
00:41:54,730 --> 00:41:56,660
Ki Ryuh, where's Hae Joo?

671
00:41:56,660 --> 00:41:58,500
She had to run to the broadcasting club.

672
00:41:58,500 --> 00:41:59,630
- What?
- What?

673
00:42:00,230 --> 00:42:03,670
Let's have a student from
each school be the host.

674
00:42:03,840 --> 00:42:04,840
Okay.

675
00:42:04,840 --> 00:42:07,010
We decided to have me be the host.

676
00:42:07,170 --> 00:42:08,340
What about you?

677
00:42:09,810 --> 00:42:11,180
For us...

678
00:42:16,620 --> 00:42:17,780
Excuse me.

679
00:42:29,730 --> 00:42:31,160
I'm glad you're here.

680
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:35,270
Which of you do you think
should host the show?

681
00:42:35,430 --> 00:42:37,070
Maybe Hae Joo should do it.

682
00:42:37,370 --> 00:42:39,740
She's smart and speaks...

683
00:42:39,740 --> 00:42:41,170
with a Seoul accent.

684
00:42:41,310 --> 00:42:43,810
And she's pretty and tall.

685
00:42:45,210 --> 00:42:46,310
She's perfect.

686
00:42:47,880 --> 00:42:51,680
I believe Jung Hee should do it.

687
00:42:52,650 --> 00:42:54,490
This is Daegu.

688
00:42:55,650 --> 00:42:57,490
I believe Jung Hee who speaks...

689
00:42:57,490 --> 00:43:00,360
with a pretty Daegu accent
should be the host.

690
00:43:00,360 --> 00:43:01,960
Jung Hee, what do you think?

691
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:08,030
Obviously, I want to do it...

692
00:43:08,200 --> 00:43:09,530
with Jin.

693
00:43:12,270 --> 00:43:14,970
- I think Hae Joo...
- I also think...

694
00:43:16,170 --> 00:43:18,480
Jung Hee should do it.

695
00:43:19,480 --> 00:43:23,150
It's a joint broadcast representing Daegu,

696
00:43:27,650 --> 00:43:31,160
so the host should show off Daegu's charm.

697
00:43:31,260 --> 00:43:34,530
Jin is looking at me.

698
00:43:34,530 --> 00:43:36,090
Only at me.

699
00:43:36,360 --> 00:43:37,800
Then let's do that.

700
00:43:38,830 --> 00:43:40,000
Okay.

701
00:43:40,930 --> 00:43:42,330
Let's work hard.

702
00:43:45,640 --> 00:43:46,810
Thank you.

703
00:43:49,170 --> 00:43:50,340
Thank you.

704
00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:54,380
Thank you.

705
00:44:00,420 --> 00:44:01,450
Hae Joo.

706
00:44:02,750 --> 00:44:04,020
I'm sorry.

707
00:44:04,820 --> 00:44:05,890
What?

708
00:44:08,130 --> 00:44:10,600
No. You're great.

709
00:44:12,330 --> 00:44:14,600
I can't wait for the broadcast.

710
00:44:14,730 --> 00:44:16,330
That's not it.

711
00:44:17,800 --> 00:44:21,470
I really am shameless.

712
00:44:28,680 --> 00:44:31,120
Let's meet by Daeil Books
at Jungang Market.

713
00:44:31,780 --> 00:44:33,690
I'll wait until 5:30.

714
00:44:34,990 --> 00:44:37,190
Hae Joo. I have to go.

715
00:44:37,390 --> 00:44:38,420
What?

716
00:44:38,860 --> 00:44:39,960
Jung Hee.

717
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:44,300
Sir.

718
00:44:45,230 --> 00:44:46,570
Here.

719
00:44:47,100 --> 00:44:48,270
Get home safely.

720
00:44:53,610 --> 00:44:54,840
Hello.

721
00:44:59,010 --> 00:45:00,380
I can't give you medicine.

722
00:45:00,750 --> 00:45:02,380
The pharmacist is out.

723
00:45:04,120 --> 00:45:05,180
I see.

724
00:45:09,350 --> 00:45:12,860
Our school is having a broadcasting show.

725
00:45:19,660 --> 00:45:21,900
Here's an invitation.

726
00:45:26,840 --> 00:45:29,470
Okay. I'll give it to the pharmacist.

727
00:45:29,470 --> 00:45:31,710
No, it's for you, mister.

728
00:45:36,250 --> 00:45:38,620
You fixed our gutter last time.

729
00:45:39,450 --> 00:45:40,820
I wanted to thank you.

730
00:45:44,720 --> 00:45:47,360
Please come if you have time.

731
00:45:51,430 --> 00:45:52,730
Where's Eng Cho?

732
00:45:53,400 --> 00:45:55,270
Did she go somewhere?

733
00:45:57,070 --> 00:45:58,240
She's napping.

734
00:45:58,540 --> 00:46:00,110
I see.

735
00:46:02,440 --> 00:46:03,480
Okay then.

736
00:46:06,610 --> 00:46:07,850
Also,

737
00:46:11,120 --> 00:46:12,380
I'm not a "mister".

738
00:46:19,360 --> 00:46:20,630
Have a nice day.

739
00:46:37,410 --> 00:46:39,880
(Jeonghyeon and Gyeryoon
Joint Broadcast Show)

740
00:46:40,380 --> 00:46:41,650
Park Hae Joo.

741
00:46:50,660 --> 00:46:53,660
Jung Hee, you brat. Why
didn't you see it sooner?

742
00:46:57,460 --> 00:46:58,530
Jin!

743
00:47:05,270 --> 00:47:07,970
I only saw this now.

744
00:47:08,640 --> 00:47:10,210
Did you wait long?

745
00:47:10,810 --> 00:47:11,980
I'm sorry.

746
00:47:11,980 --> 00:47:14,910
It's okay. You're all wet.

747
00:47:17,320 --> 00:47:18,650
It's okay.

748
00:47:18,820 --> 00:47:19,990
But sorry,

749
00:47:20,720 --> 00:47:22,420
I have to go tutor.

750
00:47:25,360 --> 00:47:28,260
Here. Take this with you.

751
00:47:28,730 --> 00:47:30,000
What about you?

752
00:47:30,060 --> 00:47:32,960
I'm fine. Don't fall again.

753
00:47:33,970 --> 00:47:35,100
See you again.

754
00:47:44,080 --> 00:47:48,080
Jin just wanted to see me one more time.

755
00:47:49,180 --> 00:47:50,420
I'm sure of it.

756
00:48:02,390 --> 00:48:04,730
I could see deep in his eyes...

757
00:48:05,100 --> 00:48:06,730
just how...

758
00:48:07,400 --> 00:48:08,930
he felt.

759
00:48:10,870 --> 00:48:12,000
Have you gone insane?

760
00:48:12,000 --> 00:48:13,470
Can't you see it stopped raining?

761
00:48:15,070 --> 00:48:16,840
- I see.
- What?

762
00:48:17,340 --> 00:48:20,750
Then why are you walking
with the umbrella open?

763
00:48:21,980 --> 00:48:24,220
It's none of your business.

764
00:48:29,350 --> 00:48:31,020
She's completely insane.

765
00:48:31,590 --> 00:48:34,490
She's gone insane after chasing Jin.

766
00:48:35,490 --> 00:48:36,800
Jung Hee.

767
00:48:38,000 --> 00:48:40,930
Wait. Does she still like Jin?

768
00:48:42,470 --> 00:48:43,640
"Still"?

769
00:48:44,000 --> 00:48:46,810
She's falling deeper and deeper.

770
00:48:46,810 --> 00:48:49,570
She'll be crying her heart out soon.

771
00:49:04,460 --> 00:49:06,590
Here's an invitation.

772
00:49:06,890 --> 00:49:09,630
Please come if you have time.

773
00:49:10,000 --> 00:49:11,300
I'm not a "mister".

774
00:49:17,470 --> 00:49:18,600
Young Choon.

775
00:49:19,170 --> 00:49:20,240
Long time no see.

776
00:49:22,440 --> 00:49:24,210
You heard I got out, right?

777
00:49:24,940 --> 00:49:26,010
Ae Sook told you.

778
00:49:26,480 --> 00:49:29,280
I heard you ignored her when she told you.

779
00:49:29,680 --> 00:49:30,850
Is that right?

780
00:49:33,320 --> 00:49:36,760
Come on. A gangster
doesn't become a saint...

781
00:49:36,760 --> 00:49:38,090
by living like this.

782
00:49:42,990 --> 00:49:44,030
Move.

783
00:49:45,160 --> 00:49:46,570
You coward.

784
00:49:52,640 --> 00:49:53,640
What?

785
00:49:56,780 --> 00:49:57,780
Happy?

786
00:49:57,880 --> 00:49:58,880
Go.

787
00:50:07,790 --> 00:50:09,620
Young Choon. That hurts.

788
00:50:09,620 --> 00:50:10,720
Hey, "friend".

789
00:50:11,860 --> 00:50:14,160
Don't mess with me. I'll kill you.

790
00:50:22,230 --> 00:50:23,340
Jung Hee.

791
00:50:24,470 --> 00:50:25,700
What are you doing?

792
00:50:29,980 --> 00:50:30,980
Auntie.

793
00:50:33,750 --> 00:50:34,750
What...

794
00:50:36,180 --> 00:50:38,180
Gosh.

795
00:50:39,020 --> 00:50:42,420
Oh my gosh. Are you just getting home?

796
00:50:47,990 --> 00:50:49,230
Why didn't you come?

797
00:50:50,560 --> 00:50:52,200
I'm sorry.

798
00:50:52,500 --> 00:50:53,700
Do you...

799
00:50:55,230 --> 00:50:57,400
Are you just getting home?

800
00:50:57,400 --> 00:50:58,400
Yes.

801
00:50:58,400 --> 00:51:01,010
Gosh. Did you drink...

802
00:51:01,210 --> 00:51:02,440
again?

803
00:51:02,440 --> 00:51:03,580
What?

804
00:51:04,210 --> 00:51:05,610
Are you sleeping already?

805
00:51:05,840 --> 00:51:07,250
Darn it.

806
00:51:08,450 --> 00:51:11,150
Why is he complaining about my sleeping?

807
00:51:13,820 --> 00:51:15,820
What are you doing at this hour?

808
00:51:16,350 --> 00:51:18,090
Something spilled here.

809
00:51:19,520 --> 00:51:20,690
What spilled?

810
00:51:22,390 --> 00:51:23,900
Did you eat?

811
00:51:49,350 --> 00:51:52,060
(Joint Broadcast Show)

812
00:51:54,830 --> 00:51:57,260
(Joint Broadcast Show)

813
00:52:05,170 --> 00:52:06,170
Hello.

814
00:52:06,570 --> 00:52:09,470
I'm Son Jin, a senior at Gyeryoon High,

815
00:52:09,470 --> 00:52:11,880
and I'll be hosting with
Lee Jung Hee today.

816
00:52:11,880 --> 00:52:14,050
Lee Jung Hee!

817
00:52:24,420 --> 00:52:25,420
Jung Hee.

818
00:52:26,120 --> 00:52:28,430
The club president said to go home...

819
00:52:28,430 --> 00:52:29,730
and get rested up.

820
00:52:30,200 --> 00:52:31,330
I'm fine.

821
00:52:32,500 --> 00:52:34,900
Go home, and rest.

822
00:52:34,900 --> 00:52:37,200
That way, your voice
will be nice and fresh.

823
00:52:37,470 --> 00:52:39,910
And you'll look prettier.

824
00:52:40,970 --> 00:52:43,840
Then maybe I'll go to the bath house.

825
00:52:44,240 --> 00:52:45,880
Yes, that would be good.

826
00:52:59,090 --> 00:53:00,190
Jung Hee.

827
00:53:00,560 --> 00:53:01,790
Jung Hee.

828
00:53:02,130 --> 00:53:04,300
- What is it?
- "What is it?"

829
00:53:04,330 --> 00:53:05,960
It isn't much.

830
00:53:06,570 --> 00:53:08,000
I wanted to thank you.

831
00:53:09,530 --> 00:53:11,700
My probation ended today.

832
00:53:11,700 --> 00:53:15,340
Thanks to you, I wasted away in detention.

833
00:53:15,340 --> 00:53:18,510
I have a nice red mark
on my transcript too.

834
00:53:18,810 --> 00:53:20,110
I told you, it wasn't me.

835
00:53:20,110 --> 00:53:22,450
I didn't tell the teacher on you.

836
00:53:22,450 --> 00:53:24,220
Sure, whatever.

837
00:53:24,380 --> 00:53:25,720
Jung Hee.

838
00:53:26,120 --> 00:53:28,920
I hear you're hosting the broadcast show.

839
00:53:30,160 --> 00:53:33,190
- Why?
- What perfect timing.

840
00:53:33,490 --> 00:53:35,030
Timing for what?

841
00:53:35,930 --> 00:53:39,360
For you to take the stage
with all of your teeth...

842
00:53:39,460 --> 00:53:41,800
knocked out.

843
00:53:44,900 --> 00:53:46,970
Let go.

844
00:53:46,970 --> 00:53:49,410
Jung Hee. Clench your teeth.

845
00:53:49,570 --> 00:53:50,680
Mr. Oh!

846
00:53:51,810 --> 00:53:53,180
- Get her.
- Jung Hee!

847
00:53:53,180 --> 00:53:54,610
- Jung Hee!
- Jung Hee!

848
00:53:54,610 --> 00:53:56,950
- Jung Hee!
- Stop!

849
00:53:56,950 --> 00:53:58,750
Jung Hee!

850
00:53:59,180 --> 00:54:01,620
- Stop!
- Get back here!

851
00:54:01,620 --> 00:54:03,360
- Stop!
- No!

852
00:54:03,620 --> 00:54:05,190
Stop chasing me!

853
00:54:05,920 --> 00:54:07,560
How long will you chase me?

854
00:54:07,560 --> 00:54:10,000
Stop, Jung Hee! Stop right there!

855
00:54:10,000 --> 00:54:11,860
Stop right there!

856
00:54:11,900 --> 00:54:13,030
No!

857
00:54:13,030 --> 00:54:14,970
- Stop chasing me!
- Stop!

858
00:54:15,770 --> 00:54:17,370
Stay away from me!

859
00:54:17,370 --> 00:54:20,840
If I catch you, I'll rip you to shreds.

860
00:54:33,090 --> 00:54:34,390
Darn it.

861
00:54:34,620 --> 00:54:35,790
Darn it.

862
00:54:36,220 --> 00:54:37,890
Are you playing with us?

863
00:54:39,120 --> 00:54:40,760
You're a pretty good runner.

864
00:54:41,160 --> 00:54:43,600
Try running all you can.

865
00:54:43,700 --> 00:54:45,160
You're in the palm of my hand.

866
00:54:45,160 --> 00:54:46,360
Don't come any closer.

867
00:54:47,230 --> 00:54:48,570
"Don't come closer"?

868
00:54:49,170 --> 00:54:51,070
Keep going. It's water.

869
00:54:51,070 --> 00:54:52,540
Don't come closer. I'll really fall in.

870
00:54:52,540 --> 00:54:55,070
Then fall in. You'll fall in, not me.

871
00:54:55,540 --> 00:54:57,110
Are you insane?

872
00:54:57,110 --> 00:54:59,180
I'm not insane, you are.

873
00:54:59,180 --> 00:55:01,280
Was it fun, tattling on me to the teacher?

874
00:55:01,280 --> 00:55:02,750
What do you take me for?

875
00:55:06,320 --> 00:55:07,820
Did you just duck?

876
00:55:09,450 --> 00:55:10,820
Hold her down.

877
00:55:10,820 --> 00:55:12,660
You psycho.

878
00:55:12,890 --> 00:55:14,760
- Jung Hee!
- Stop it!

879
00:55:14,760 --> 00:55:15,760
Hey!

880
00:55:15,990 --> 00:55:17,330
Why you...

881
00:55:28,340 --> 00:55:29,570
Help me!

882
00:55:32,080 --> 00:55:34,580
- Someone help me!
- Look at her.

883
00:55:35,380 --> 00:55:36,520
Are you a frog?

884
00:55:36,520 --> 00:55:38,480
I really can't swim!

885
00:55:38,480 --> 00:55:41,250
Jung Hee really can't swim.

886
00:55:43,360 --> 00:55:45,460
Hey. You go in.

887
00:55:45,460 --> 00:55:46,960
I can't swim.

888
00:55:49,430 --> 00:55:52,930
Jin. I guess this is how I die.

889
00:55:52,930 --> 00:55:55,300
I didn't get to share my love with you.

890
00:55:55,300 --> 00:55:57,370
I guess I'm going to die first.

891
00:55:57,470 --> 00:55:59,910
She's drowning! Oh, no!

892
00:56:03,680 --> 00:56:05,740
Jin?

893
00:56:06,140 --> 00:56:07,280
Jung Hee!

894
00:56:07,510 --> 00:56:08,810
Jung Hee!

895
00:56:14,650 --> 00:56:15,890
Jin.

896
00:56:35,840 --> 00:56:37,310
I'm so happy.

897
00:56:37,910 --> 00:56:40,980
I can die now, and I'll be happy.

898
00:56:59,600 --> 00:57:02,270
Jung Hee. Wake up.

899
00:57:02,770 --> 00:57:04,200
Jung Hee.

900
00:57:04,640 --> 00:57:06,400
Jung Hee.

901
00:57:06,400 --> 00:57:08,810
You need to give her CPR.

902
00:57:09,210 --> 00:57:10,710
Do it.

903
00:57:10,710 --> 00:57:12,640
What did they say to do?

904
00:57:12,640 --> 00:57:13,910
I don't know.

905
00:57:14,310 --> 00:57:17,350
Get the water out. Press down on her chest.

906
00:57:17,350 --> 00:57:18,820
That's right. Get the water out!

907
00:57:18,820 --> 00:57:20,290
You do it then!

908
00:57:20,290 --> 00:57:21,420
- You do it!
- You do it!

909
00:57:21,420 --> 00:57:24,260
- You do it!
- Hurry!

910
00:57:24,620 --> 00:57:27,260
How can I do that?

911
00:57:27,430 --> 00:57:29,260
You do it.

912
00:57:30,100 --> 00:57:31,100
- Hey.
- You do it.

913
00:57:31,100 --> 00:57:32,800
Hey!

914
00:57:34,400 --> 00:57:35,800
Darn it.

915
00:57:37,140 --> 00:57:38,300
Jung Hee.

916
00:57:38,700 --> 00:57:40,740
Don't die. Jung Hee.

917
00:57:45,080 --> 00:57:46,110
Jung Hee.

918
00:57:46,680 --> 00:57:47,780
Sorry.

919
00:57:48,550 --> 00:57:50,780
I'll take care of you no matter what.

920
00:58:07,330 --> 00:58:09,170
Jung Hee.

921
00:58:11,740 --> 00:58:12,770
Jung Hee.

922
00:58:14,270 --> 00:58:16,740
Jung Hee. No, no, no.

923
00:58:16,740 --> 00:58:18,410
Jung Hee.

924
00:58:21,580 --> 00:58:22,680
No.

925
00:58:25,080 --> 00:58:26,650
Mouth-to-mouth.

926
00:58:28,950 --> 00:58:30,020
Commencing.

927
00:58:41,170 --> 00:58:44,170
Is this... Mouth-to-mouth?

928
00:58:44,740 --> 00:58:48,010
Does that mean these are Jin's lips?

929
00:58:53,980 --> 00:58:56,850
Jung Hee! Jung Hee, are you okay?

930
00:58:56,920 --> 00:58:59,280
Are you awake? Jung Hee.

931
00:58:59,550 --> 00:59:02,020
You're alive. You're alive. Jung Hee.

932
00:59:02,150 --> 00:59:04,920
I'm so glad. You're alive.

933
00:59:06,490 --> 00:59:08,160
I was so scared.

934
00:59:08,490 --> 00:59:10,000
I'm so glad.

935
00:59:28,980 --> 00:59:31,680
Mom! Jung Hee's awake!

936
00:59:32,020 --> 00:59:33,120
- What?
- Jung Hee!

937
00:59:33,190 --> 00:59:35,290
My baby girl!

938
00:59:35,720 --> 00:59:37,490
Are you finally awake?

939
00:59:37,490 --> 00:59:39,420
- Jung Hee.
- Mom.

940
00:59:39,860 --> 00:59:42,630
- Where am I?
- It's a hospital! Look!

941
00:59:43,160 --> 00:59:45,000
You brat!

942
00:59:45,300 --> 00:59:47,330
Do we not have water...

943
00:59:47,330 --> 00:59:49,470
at the house?

944
00:59:49,470 --> 00:59:51,970
Why were you drinking water from the river?

945
00:59:53,640 --> 00:59:56,270
- Where's Jin?
- What about him?

946
00:59:56,270 --> 00:59:58,510
Where's Jin, who saved me?

947
00:59:58,840 --> 01:00:01,280
You brat. Don't even get me started.

948
01:00:01,280 --> 01:00:03,280
Because of you, you brat,

949
01:00:03,280 --> 01:00:05,120
another family's precious son...

950
01:00:05,120 --> 01:00:07,920
almost drowned and died.

951
01:00:07,920 --> 01:00:09,390
How can I face his parents now?

952
01:00:09,390 --> 01:00:12,160
Dong Moon is hospitalized next door!
Dong Moon!

953
01:00:14,290 --> 01:00:16,700
No way. The one who saved me...

954
01:00:16,700 --> 01:00:20,070
You may have died if not for Dong Moon.

955
01:00:31,910 --> 01:00:33,550
Shoot.

956
01:00:34,410 --> 01:00:36,820
Shoot. That's right.

957
01:00:37,520 --> 01:00:40,020
- I have to take a bath.
- You crazy wench!

958
01:00:40,020 --> 01:00:42,820
You want to go into water again?

959
01:00:42,820 --> 01:00:45,020
I have to take a bath
before tomorrow's show.

960
01:00:45,020 --> 01:00:46,830
The broadcast show ended already!

961
01:00:46,830 --> 01:00:49,030
What do you mean? It's tomorrow.

962
01:00:49,690 --> 01:00:51,400
Today is "tomorrow".

963
01:00:51,560 --> 01:00:54,530
You slept for over a day!

964
01:00:55,000 --> 01:00:57,670
- Today is "tomorrow"?
- That's right.

965
01:00:58,270 --> 01:00:59,470
Is that true?

966
01:01:00,110 --> 01:01:02,140
- It is.
- No.

967
01:01:02,510 --> 01:01:04,540
No. No!

968
01:01:04,740 --> 01:01:05,940
No what?

969
01:01:06,510 --> 01:01:09,180
- Hey! Hey!
- Hey! Jung Hee!

970
01:01:09,350 --> 01:01:11,780
Get back here!

971
01:01:16,860 --> 01:01:18,620
Get your act together, you brat!

972
01:01:47,150 --> 01:01:48,490
It really...

973
01:01:50,860 --> 01:01:52,720
is over.

974
01:02:00,570 --> 01:02:01,670
Hae Joo.

975
01:02:02,600 --> 01:02:03,800
Don't do this.

976
01:02:06,240 --> 01:02:07,840
Please don't do this.

977
01:02:09,910 --> 01:02:11,840
Can't you think it over?

978
01:02:13,550 --> 01:02:14,680
I'm sorry.

979
01:02:15,780 --> 01:02:17,020
Why...

980
01:02:17,720 --> 01:02:19,420
don't you understand how I feel?

981
01:02:23,290 --> 01:02:24,690
Jin.

982
01:02:26,060 --> 01:02:27,160
Hae Joo?

983
01:02:29,690 --> 01:02:30,860
Are they...

984
01:02:32,060 --> 01:02:33,500
dating?

985
01:02:34,830 --> 01:02:36,330
Did Jin...

986
01:02:37,400 --> 01:02:39,540
fall for her too?

987
01:02:47,580 --> 01:02:48,750
Jung Hee.
